    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a reliable ride that\u2019s perfect for your daily commute! This vehicle is in fair condition, showing some honest signs of character and use, but it remains a solid and dependable choice for anyone looking for great value. It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready to hit the road with its next owner today!",
